metadata.name: BunnyMunny
metadata.description: Enter a world of mythical wealth, prosperity, and positive energy with the limited edition Bunny Munny NFT. This exclusive NFT is more than just a mere trinket - it's a talisman of good fortune, granting its lucky owner access to a realm of untold opportunities, including exclusive drops and the mystical world of Bunny Munny and all around good luck!
